5
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,296
♪ Whether you're light or a lie,
I can't pull myself away ♪

6
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:46,760
♪ In this game,
truth or lie no longer matters ♪

7
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:51,976
[Queen of Darkness]

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[Episode 24]

9
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,000
You sneaky woman.

10
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,520
How dare you hurt me!

11
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,496
Call an ambulance now!

12
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:02,960
Otherwise,

13
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,800
I'll make you pay dearly!

14
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,800
That An Ning who swallowed her pride
is long gone.

15
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,160
You're not Ye Ying.

16
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,656
Stop imitating her.

17
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,736
You know what?

18
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,976
You're nothing but a complete copy.

19
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:27,617
What's wrong?

20
00:01:27,641 --> 00:01:29,896
Think a tiny knife is enough
to scare me?

21
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,817
You'll never

22
00:01:30,841 --> 00:01:32,536
never become Ye Ying!

23
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,000
You're right, I'm not her.

24
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,456
But Ye Ying
gave me a chance to survive.

25
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,976
She helped me break free and start over.

26
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,376
The Song family pushed me to the edge.

27
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,736
You cheated and abused me.

28
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:43,416
Mom is cruel and petty.

29
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:45,680
I hid in the shadows, living like a ghost.

30
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,336
All for this moment

31
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,040
to take revenge on you!

32
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,400
You

33
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,056
you wouldn't

34
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:55,000
really kill me, right?

35
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,680
Letting you die

36
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,400
would be too easy.

37
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,536
Every slap you gave me.

38
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,760
Every ounce of pain.

39
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,776
Today,

40
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,736
you'll taste it all back!

41
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:09,760
Go to hell!

42
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,696
Gather all officers in the station now.

43
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,336
Find Ye Ying and Song Pa's location.

44
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:22,816
Legal or illegal,

45
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,816
just use any means necessary.

46
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,696
I'll take full responsibility.

47
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,297
Boss.

48
00:02:25,321 --> 00:02:26,976
I know you worry about Miss Ye.

49
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,256
But this is overstepping your authority.

50
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,480
It'll cause a huge stir.

51
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,496
If anything happens to her,

52
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,600
I'll stake my life on it.

53
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,160
Everything else,

54
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,480
I don't care.

55
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,400
Inspector Huo.

56
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,296
We've received a report.

57
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,136
[Immediate suspension] Accusing you of

58
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,977
[pending investigation]
corruption and misconduct.

59
00:02:42,001 --> 00:02:43,296
You are hereby suspended
for investigation.

60
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,320
Please come with us.

61
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,376
Suspending me just because of

62
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,480
an unconfirmed report?

63
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,440
How much did Song Pa pay you?

64
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,576
We're just following orders.

65
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,400
You can appeal
if you think there's a mistake.

66
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,280
What are you doing?

67
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,416
Does this feel familiar?

68
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,760
We're back here again.

69
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,536
Now Jiang Meng is dead.

70
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,720
And the evidence is gone too.

71
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,856
Honestly, I can't imagine

72
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:40,016
what else

73
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,616
can you do to fight back?

74
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,656
You've done so many shady things.

75
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,776
There'll always be traces left behind.

76
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,256
Even if I die,

77
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,920
Huo Xiao will keep digging for the truth.

78
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,296
Huo Xiao has been suspended
for investigation.

79
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,416
He can barely save himself.

80
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,616
How could he help you with the case?

81
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:57,176
I was being merciful
not to kill you right away.

82
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,200
You better worry about

83
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,736
how you're going to die.

84
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,760
Huo Xiao...

85
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,320
What did you do to him?

86
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,080
Don't rush.

87
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,536
Soon,

88
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,920
you'll meet him again
on the road to the afterlife.

89
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,417
Boss.

90
00:04:14,441 --> 00:04:16,136
The doctor bandaged Ti Cha.

91
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,280
He's awake now.

92
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,816
Okay.

93
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:20,840
Let him come down.

94
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,240
Dad!

95
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:28,096
Dad, dad.

96
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,936
I don't want to live anymore.

97
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,696
I'm not a man anymore!

98
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,656
Dad, dad.

99
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,560
Alright, tell me who did this to you.

100
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,440
It was An Ning.

101
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,896
An Ning did this!

102
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,176
She's back.

103
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,280
Dad.

104
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,640
Dad.

105
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,600
Dad!

106
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
It's you.

107
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,616
You must've teamed up with An Ning.

108
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,000
And set Ti Cha up, right?

109
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,320
Didn't expect karma to come this fast.

110
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,440
Since you've done so many evil things,

111
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:06,120
someone will help me
make your family end with no heirs.

112
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,136
So what if I've done evil?

113
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,056
Huo Xiao's father never knew
what was good for him

114
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,416
and got in the way of my money.

115
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,296
Ye Hong refused the merger

116
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,336
and even threatened me with.

117
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,776
Longxing Group's gang crime business.

118
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,920
The An family was even stupider.

119
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,576
Clinging to those group shares.

120
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,640
Thinking they could take the company
back from me.

121
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,536
But in the end?

122
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,016
All those who opposed me

123
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,736
ended up with

124
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,216
no proper burial.

125
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,616
Huo Xiao has transferred
all his shares to An Ning.

126
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,256
Even if we all die,

127
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,680
you'll never get Longxing Group.

128
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,656
Longxing Group?

129
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,560
That's just a cover.

130
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,856
The global illegal business group
I control

131
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,200
is the real big business.

132
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,016
I've bribed all systems,

133
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,176
including the police force.

134
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:54,776
With those systems clearing my path,

135
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,296
my way to profit

136
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:58,480
is completely unobstructed.

137
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,576
Just for gain,

138
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,240
you've killed so many innocent lives.

139
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,680
You're nothing but a heartless monster!

140
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,216
Being a monster

141
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,376
is still better than

142
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,656
being weak.

143
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,936
I've run out of patience.

144
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:12,777
You

145
00:06:12,801 --> 00:06:14,456
should take your final walk.

146
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:17,416
Go find your so-called justice
in the afterlife.

147
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,320
I'll remember your face clearly.

148
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,696
Even as a ghost, I won't let you go.

149
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,720
Good.

150
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,016
Let's see

151
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,840
how exactly you won't let me go.

152
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,880
Kill her.

153
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,480
You...

154
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,640
Huo Xiao.

155
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,297
I thought you were already...

156
00:06:47,321 --> 00:06:48,520
You'll never know

157
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,536
who the real winner is

158
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,896
until the end.

159
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:55,256
All the crimes you just confessed to

160
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,960
have been livestreamed
across the internet.

161
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,600
Turn around.

162
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,336
I heard them report to Song Pa

163
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,360
that they caught you.

164
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,640
Okay.

165
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,376
Don't let anyone know
I left the station yet.

166
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,560
We can't alert them too soon.

167
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,800
Got it.

168
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,160
[An Ning]

169
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,296
Song Pa sent Ti Cha a message,

170
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,217
saying he caught Ye Ying

171
00:07:38,241 --> 00:07:39,921
and is on his way
back to the Song mansion.

172
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,560
Ye Ying.

173
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,697
Huo Xiao?

174
00:08:03,721 --> 00:08:04,920
Why are you here?

175
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,440
- Are you okay?
- Are you alright?

176
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,656
What do we do now?

177
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,360
All the evidence is gone.

178
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,096
Only Song Pa's confession

179
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,920
can bring him to justice.

180
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,576
I've already

181
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,840
set up cameras in advance.

182
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,056
I know what you're trying to do.

183
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,080
Leave it to me.

184
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,680
Police?

185
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,720
How did it end up like this?

186
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,080
An Ning!

187
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,520
Take him down!

188
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,760
You okay?

189
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,656
Looks like today

190
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,440
we might not make it out alive.

191
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,080
Scared?

192
00:09:19,135 --> 00:09:39,235
Officail Website : kissasia.id  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

193
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,160
No.

194
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,320
I'll never lose you again.

195
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,440
Out of bullets, huh?

196
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,576
At death's door

197
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,040
and still being lovey-dovey?

198
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,000
Don't move!

199
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,960
Put down your weapon!

200
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:07,096
An Ning has submitted
evidence of your crimes.

201
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,656
The chief has signed the arrest warrant.

202
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,416
Resisting will only lead to death!

203
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,257
Don't move!

204
00:10:11,281 --> 00:10:12,601
If anyone moves, I'll shoot them.

205
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,416
You hired killers to

206
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,720
murder my father Ye Hong.

207
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:16,977
I've waited too long

208
00:10:17,001 --> 00:10:18,296
to settle this blood debt.

209
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,160
Today is the day you pay for it.

210
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,440
You seized group interests.

211
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,936
Stay back!

212
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,096
You're completely out of your mind.

213
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,360
You staged accidents to silence people.

214
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,680
I endured in the darkness.

215
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,640
All for this very moment

216
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,360
to tear you apart completely.

217
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,360
Now, meet your end!

218
00:10:37,730 --> 00:10:39,166
♪ Keep watching me ♪

219
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:43,620
♪ Run out of strength,
staring fixedly on me ♪

220
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:49,030
♪ Don't look away, keep watching me ♪

221
00:10:49,130 --> 00:10:52,270
♪ Keep watching me ♪

222
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,400
Welcome back, Chairman An.

223
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,737
Let me make a statement.

224
00:10:59,761 --> 00:11:01,400
It's about our group's ten-year plan.

225
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,480
Ying, thank you.

226
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:15,096
You've carried too much for me.

227
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,240
I'll do everything I can
to make it up to you.

228
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:18,976
Sis,

229
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,936
back then human traffickers targeted us.

230
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,376
You lured them away alone to save me,

231
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,976
and we were separated for years.

232
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,016
Now that Father has passed away,

233
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,496
we went through so much.

234
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,536
I never thought

235
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:31,496
we'd meet again.

236
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,160
And even stay by each other's side.

237
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:35,400
That's already healed so many regrets.

238
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,216
Sis.

239
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,560
It's time for me to find my own path.

240
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,016
Dad.

241
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,296
Song Pa has finally faced justice.

242
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,257
Now,

243
00:11:51,281 --> 00:11:52,760
you can rest in peace.

244
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,280
Boss.

245
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,520
Thanks to all your trust.

246
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,520
I officially take over as the new Leader.

247
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,256
From this day on,

248
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:13,920
Qingyun Gang will never
engage in illegal activities.

249
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,056
If I, Ye Ying, ever break this vow,

250
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,400
may heaven and earth destroy me.

251
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:21,576
A major gang crime case was recently
solved in the city.

252
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:25,160
The crime group led by Song Pa
has been completely wiped out.

253
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:42,840
Why not sleep a bit longer?

254
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,680
It's already morning.

255
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:51,840
What are you up to again?

256
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:53,560
Getting my breakfast.

257
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:56,520
Stop messing around.

258
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,616
Some people

259
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:05,576
burn their bridges
once they've crossed them.

260
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,080
Not answering calls.

261
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,040
Nowhere to be found.

262
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,536
I have no choice

263
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,440
but to seize every second.

264
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,720
I was just busy.

265
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:20,496
Then when Leader Ye
finally has some free time,

266
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,000
maybe pay a bit more attention to me?

267
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,200
Is this enough?

268
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,440
What about this?

269
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,720
How about…

270
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,240
How about what?

271
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,240
How about…

272
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,280
How about…

273
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,040
How about letting the night

274
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,000
fall once more?

275
00:13:57,540 --> 00:14:03,310
♪ Hold me tight,
let the darkness drown me ♪

276
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:10,700
♪ Even one second of truth is enough
to lose myself in it ♪

277
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:17,420
♪ Whether you're light or a lie,
I can't pull myself away ♪

278
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,736
♪ In this game,
truth or lie no longer matters ♪

279
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:23,970
[The End]

280
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:43,450
♪ Mist coils around the sleeping forest ♪

281
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:47,100
♪ Memories scattered
through cracks of darkness ♪

282
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:50,950
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

283
00:14:54,490 --> 00:14:57,750
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

284
00:14:57,980 --> 00:15:01,310
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

285
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:04,880
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

286
00:15:07,190 --> 00:15:14,260
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

287
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:18,296
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

288
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:21,896
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

289
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:24,856
♪ Burn like fire ♪

290
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:28,290
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

291
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:32,400
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

292
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:35,116
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

293
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:38,280
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

294
00:15:38,570 --> 00:15:42,070
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

295
00:15:42,140 --> 00:15:48,600
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

296
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:52,576
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

297
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:56,120
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

298
00:15:56,340 --> 00:16:02,870
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

299
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:05,130
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

